io.druid.query

Class Druids.TimeBoundaryQueryBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.druid.query.Druids.TimeBoundaryQueryBuilder
  • Enclosing class:
    Druids

    public static class Druids.TimeBoundaryQueryBuilder
extends Object
    A Builder for TimeBoundaryQuery. Required: dataSource() must be called before build() Usage example: 
    
   TimeBoundaryQuery query = new MaxTimeQueryBuilder()
                                  .dataSource("Example")
                                  .build();
    See Also:
    TimeBoundaryQuery
